t\tZapier + Gmail parser + Sheets + Data Studio\tWeekly P&L report, cash flow projection, metric dashboard 🔷 MARKETING AUTOMATION WORKFLOWS Campaign Type\tTrigger Event\tAutomation Sequence\tPlatforms\tConversion Optimization Welcome Series\tEmail opt-in\t1. Instant: Lead magnet delivery 2. Day 1: Welcome + brand story 3. Day 3: Value content 4. Day 5: Soft product intro 5. Day 7: Offer + urgency\tActiveCampaign/Klaviyo + Canva (email templates)\tSegment based on email opens, click behavior → Dynamic content insertion Abandoned Cart Recovery\tCart abandonment (15 min)\t1. 15 min: SMS reminder 2. 2 hours: Email #1 + product benefits 3. 24 hours: Email #2 + social proof 4. 48 hours: Email #3 + 10% discount 5. 72 hours: Final urgency email\tShopify + Klaviyo + Twilio SMS + Canva\tDiscount code auto-generation, countdown timer, personalized product recommendations Post-Purchase Upsell\tOrder confirmation\t1. Immediate: Thank you email + OTO offer 2. 7 days: Product usage tips 3. 14 days: Complementary product suggestion 4. 30 days: Review request 5. 45 days: Replenishment/upgrade offer\tThriveCart/Shopify + ActiveCampaign + Go High Level\tTrigger based on order value, tag high-value customers, create lookalike audiences Webinar Funnel\tWebinar registration\t1. Instant: Confirmation + calendar invite 2. Day before: Reminder #1 3. 1 hour before: Reminder #2 + Zoom link 4. During: Automated slides + offers 5. Post: Replay + limited offer\tZoom + Go High Level + Google Calendar + ThriveCart\tAttendance tracking, engagement scoring, automatic segmentation for buyers/non-buyers 🔷 ECOMMERCE AUTOMATION SYSTEM Business Function\tAutomation Workflow\tInput Data\tMicro-Steps\tOutput & Metrics Product Research → Launch\tTrend identification to live listing\tNiche keywords, competitor analysis\t1. Pinterest/Etsy trend scraping 2. AI design generation (Canva API) 3. Mockup creation (Printify) 4. SEO optimization (ChatGPT API) 5. Auto-publish to Shopify 6. Social media posts scheduled